st.write("\nTraditionally, civil engineers rely on a 28-day waiting period to assess the strength of concrete by subjecting concrete samples to pressure tests using Universal Testing Machines (UTM). This process incurs time and resource costs, including the use of UTM equipment, power consumption, and material expenses.")
